  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Close Call Extreme is a fast, stylish arcade dodger where you slip through traffic, skim past bumpers by a pixel, and chase those long, heart-pounding high-score runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every close call matters, and one mistake might end it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752530/extras/8e2cb87cb01b02397c09643f43ef3a8d.poster.avif?t=1770763844\" width=430 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752530/extras/8e2cb87cb01b02397c09643f43ef3a8d.webm?t=1770763844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752530/extras/8e2cb87cb01b02397c09643f43ef3a8d.mp4?t=1770763844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless, high-speed arcade driving where every near-miss boosts your score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain close calls to build massive combos and extend your run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No brakes; only speed, control, and nerve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crash takes you to pit, slows you down</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MASTER THE CLOSE CALL</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision matters more than speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track changes will test your focus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Staying calm is part of the challenge </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ONE MORE RUN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Close Call Extreme is built for short sessions, long streaks, and that <i>just one more try</i> feeling.<br>Focus, take risks, and see how far you can push it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That’s a better emotional exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Close Call Extreme is inspired by classic arcade racers and the kind of high-speed, high-focus driving games many of us grew up with, including endless racers from the C64 era like LeMans. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
